1
00:00:00,166 --> 00:00:00,966
hi

2
00:00:01,400 --> 00:00:05,100
today we are going to start an easy but long task

3
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:08,300
making a star gate in GTNH

4
00:00:09,366 --> 00:00:12,166
this pack is known for being rather easy

5
00:00:12,166 --> 00:00:15,000
so we are going to play in hardcore

6
00:00:15,366 --> 00:00:18,633
in the rare eventuality that we will die

7
00:00:18,666 --> 00:00:21,400
all we will have to do is load a backup

8
00:00:23,266 --> 00:00:26,866

the first thing we shall do is to dispose of that book


9
00:00:26,866 --> 00:00:28,233
since books are boring

10
00:00:28,233 --> 00:00:31,100
and we do not have free slots in our inventory

11
00:00:31,566 --> 00:00:34,600
we also do not have time for reading it

12
00:00:36,466 --> 00:00:40,400
we can now proceed into looking at a place with grass green enough

13
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:42,833
and then start digging our basement

14
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:47,800
now that we have found green grass

15
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:51,166
we can start to collect the resources for a bed

16
00:00:56,100 --> 00:00:59,433
this pack is not as bad as vanilla Minecraft

17
00:00:59,433 --> 00:01:02,000
but it is still not realistic enough

18
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:05,300
the bed only requires some wool and some wood

19
00:01:05,633 --> 00:01:10,266
there is no need for screws, glue or anything to hold it together

20
00:01:10,633 --> 00:01:13,500
probably it is held in place with magic

21
00:01:13,866 --> 00:01:19,833
anyways let's start gathering the required resources before the night arrives

22
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:26,466
now that we have a bed we can make some tools

23
00:01:26,866 --> 00:01:30,400
that way, we can gather materials more quickly

24
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:34,033
and we can also dig our basement into Hard Rock

25
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:40,300
we must not forget that this pack also has some quests

26
00:01:40,666 --> 00:01:42,366
let's give them a look

27
00:01:45,266 --> 00:01:48,000
yeah I'm not reading that stuff

28
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:54,966
we shall only complete the required tasks that will lead us to the star gate nothing more

29
00:02:00,966 --> 00:02:02,966
after a long day of work

30
00:02:02,966 --> 00:02:06,400
we shall have a nice sleep while watching the sunset

31
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:09,233
we will then have breakfast with an apple

32
00:02:09,233 --> 00:02:11,600
so that the doctors will stay away

33
00:02:12,666 --> 00:02:15,833
now that we have a shelter and some resources

34
00:02:15,833 --> 00:02:20,266
we can start looking into the tasks given us by the gods of the book

35
00:02:20,633 --> 00:02:23,200
since we did not follow it until now

36
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:28,200
we are rewarded with having to craft again half of the stuff we already did

37
00:02:31,233 --> 00:02:34,200
we shall now start farming some food

38
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:37,966
we will be using it as a sacrifice to the gods of the book

39
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:40,800
since we are playing in hardcore mode

40
00:02:40,833 --> 00:02:43,566
we are going to have a vegetarian diet

41
00:02:43,966 --> 00:02:44,966
that way

42
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,766
zombies and skeletons won't attack us

43
00:02:47,766 --> 00:02:50,500
as they will see us as an already dead entity

44
00:02:55,966 --> 00:02:59,433
it seems that the gods of the book won't like our diet

45
00:02:59,666 --> 00:03:02,100
they are asking us to make a sword

46
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:04,000
and slay some poor animals

47
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,766
with no apparent reason

48
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:09,266
we do not have the power for opposing the gods

49
00:03:09,266 --> 00:03:11,600
so we shall do as they say

50
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,233
as asked by the gods

51
00:03:15,233 --> 00:03:18,566
we shall slay six pigs and six sheeps

52
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,066
after a long day of fighting

53
00:03:22,066 --> 00:03:24,833
all we need is a well deserved night of sleep

54
00:03:24,833 --> 00:03:28,433
to forget about all the cruelty the gods made us do

55
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,766
or maybe not

56
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:37,166
we shall spend the night thinking about the cruelty we did when we fist arrived

57
00:03:37,366 --> 00:03:42,800
we shouldn't have thrown away the sacred book we were given during the creation of this world

58
00:03:43,166 --> 00:03:46,700
we shall spend the rest of the night digging a better basement

59
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:51,200
it appears that the gods accepted our regrets

60
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:53,833
as you can see from the gods message

61
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:58,200
it is now time to emerge back to the surface

62
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,866
and touch some grass

63
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:05,433
it appears that the gods gifted us with the blessing of some string

64
00:04:05,466 --> 00:04:09,766
we shall not forget about this incredible gift we just received

65
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:17,166
we can now go gather some more of the resources required in our path to the Star Gate

66
00:04:17,166 --> 00:04:19,200
like some wood and some gravel

67
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:23,466
we must be careful not to let any log float in the air

68
00:04:23,466 --> 00:04:26,033
or the gods may get mad at us again

69
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:33,700
we might also start making a nice looking house above our basement

70
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:36,633
so that people won't look too badly at us

71
00:04:39,366 --> 00:04:43,200
and after a long day of work we can finally sleep

72
00:04:45,233 --> 00:04:51,066
today we are going to explore this beautiful world given us by the gods of the book

73
00:04:51,466 --> 00:04:54,800
actually we are looking for some useful resources

74
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:58,266
that might helps us in our mission of making a star gate

75
00:05:00,266 --> 00:05:05,233
we have found some source of rubber and also some clay while on the way

76
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:10,466
after all of that exploration

77
00:05:10,466 --> 00:05:11,766
we shall sleep

78
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:14,600
and oh god no

79
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,433
why

80
00:05:19,666 --> 00:05:23,966
maybe that is a sign that we shall work more on our basement

81
00:05:24,366 --> 00:05:28,300
we must make it look as if a creeper exploded inside it

82
00:05:30,466 --> 00:05:33,200
it is now getting too dark in here

83
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:37,400
our only saviour could be our old friend, NEI

84
00:05:37,666 --> 00:05:41,033
let's ask him how to make glowing sticks

85
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:49,033
we are lucky we can use the resin we found earlier with string we were given by the gods

86
00:05:49,033 --> 00:05:51,633
to make the holy glowing sticks

87
00:05:51,966 --> 00:05:54,700
they are holy because they never burn out

88
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:58,566
we shall now take a few seconds 

89
00:05:58,566 --> 00:06:01,966
to appreciate how nice our basement looks

90
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:04,600
no creepers exploded in here

91
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,400
however

92
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:06,766
a creeper lives here

93
00:06:09,166 --> 00:06:12,100
and the gods rewarded us with more string

94
00:06:16,166 --> 00:06:18,300
now we can gather some clay

95
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:29,566
we can set up the start of our farm

96
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:33,100
where we will be farming cotton and wheat

97
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:36,800
that way, we will be able to produce our own string

98
00:06:36,866 --> 00:06:40,633
with out having to rely on the gifts from the gods

99
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,833
we can use wheat for our future cow farm

100
00:06:43,833 --> 00:06:46,400
and also to make food for us

101
00:06:46,633 --> 00:06:49,633
and with the newly acquired food and light source

102
00:06:49,633 --> 00:06:52,666
we can go gather some materials underground

103
00:06:52,666 --> 00:06:55,400
so that we can start building our industry

104
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:58,233
now that we have all of these resources

105
00:06:58,266 --> 00:07:01,533
I think it is a good time to have some resting sleep

106
00:07:01,533 --> 00:07:04,866
and then start building our factory of pollution

107
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:07,433
now it's time to start

108
00:07:07,433 --> 00:07:07,833
wait

109
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,700
where am I is this a dream

110
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:14,166
it looks like what I was planning to do

111
00:07:14,433 --> 00:07:16,766
it has to be an illustrative dream

112
00:07:16,766 --> 00:07:19,266
where I can explain my plans

113
00:07:20,100 --> 00:07:20,833
so be it

114
00:07:20,833 --> 00:07:23,433
here we will have a smeltery

115
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:27,666
for making bronze tier tools and the first molds

116
00:07:28,166 --> 00:07:32,766
and next to it we have the coke ovens for making creosote oil

117
00:07:33,966 --> 00:07:37,300
now I think we should go outside to touch some grass

118
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:39,500
and plan our automated farm

119
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:43,700
wait this tree looks kinda sus

120
00:07:44,566 --> 00:07:48,400
apparently Santa gifted us with some coal

121
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,700
but it looks like this coal kinda went bad

122
00:07:51,966 --> 00:07:55,700
I hope it's still good enough for our boilers

123
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:59,066
wait, wtf did just happen

124
00:07:59,366 --> 00:08:02,000
it should have not destroyed the message

125
00:08:02,466 --> 00:08:08,600
now let's heat up this spoiled coal which almost turned bad into shiny trash

126
00:08:09,233 --> 00:08:13,600
we might be able to revert it back into burnable coal by heating it up

127
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:17,766
but that could require one whole bucket of creosote oil

128
00:08:18,266 --> 00:08:19,233
please god

129
00:08:19,233 --> 00:08:22,766
make it revert back to burnable coal

130
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:33,566
okay I do not know if that worked as it should have

131
00:08:33,566 --> 00:08:36,600
but it looks like we can still burn that stuff

132
00:08:37,433 --> 00:08:38,233
now

133
00:08:38,300 --> 00:08:40,000
here we have a boiler

134
00:08:40,266 --> 00:08:42,900
it burns coal to produce steam

135
00:08:45,866 --> 00:08:49,400
great it accepted our rotten coal

136
00:08:49,566 --> 00:08:51,700
now we have to give it some water

137
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,266
let's go fetch it

138
00:08:55,866 --> 00:08:59,300
we do not want to use that murky water from a swamp

139
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:02,600
we shall go gather clean water form a river

140
00:09:11,933 --> 00:09:14,433
now that the boiler have heated up a bit

141
00:09:14,433 --> 00:09:16,500
we can finally add the water

142
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:19,000
so that we will get instantly steam

143
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,266
wait what happened

144
00:09:21,466 --> 00:09:23,633
why is it all dark

145
00:09:23,766 --> 00:09:25,800
what kind of dream is that

146
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,900
am I finally waking up

147
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:32,466
and now what is this place

148
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:35,866
it looks like we have found a way to go to heaven

149
00:09:36,666 --> 00:09:37,300
oh, wow

150
00:09:37,300 --> 00:09:42,000
so it looks like heaven is powered by nukes

151
00:09:43,666 --> 00:09:46,833
but it looks like this is not properly set it up

152
00:09:47,033 --> 00:09:49,300
let me help you God

153
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,966
if we stack the cells closer

154
00:09:52,966 --> 00:09:54,866
the output should be greater

155
00:09:54,866 --> 00:09:58,033
and we should also obtain a higher efficiency

156
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,466
like that

157
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:14,700
now we have to turn off this infernal device

158
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:17,700
wait

159
00:10:18,066 --> 00:10:19,700
what is that music

160
00:10:19,766 --> 00:10:21,566
where is it coming from

161
00:10:23,433 --> 00:10:27,866
and how can you actually die in heaven

162
00:10:28,033 --> 00:10:30,233
and now what happens

163
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:34,200
guys I have a plan B

164
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:39,200
we just reload a backup from before we had the weird dream

165
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,300
let's do it

166
00:10:41,266 --> 00:10:42,166
OK

167
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:45,166
I can't see our Star Gate mission

168
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:48,466
we can either go into a generic world

169
00:10:48,466 --> 00:10:51,800
or, yeah let's go with the mission B

170
00:10:53,466 --> 00:10:56,700
now we have to figure a way out of this ice kite thing

171
00:10:57,700 --> 00:11:00,066
this looks like a control room

172
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:02,633
here

173
00:11:02,633 --> 00:11:05,800
there are some levers that we shall randomly shuffle

174
00:11:06,033 --> 00:11:10,833
that way, God will be mad at us and send us back to our basement

175
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:14,066
and what is that weird looking pipe

176
00:11:14,366 --> 00:11:16,733
what just passed inside it

177
00:11:16,733 --> 00:11:17,466
whatever

178
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,433
okay

179
00:11:19,666 --> 00:11:22,633
it looks like nothing really happened this time

180
00:11:22,766 --> 00:11:26,366
let's look around for an universe traveling machine

181
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,500
that looks like it

182
00:11:29,666 --> 00:11:31,300
let's give it a try

183
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:39,600
hey

184
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:40,600
it worked

185
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:43,766
I'm back in the world of my dreams

186
00:11:43,866 --> 00:11:45,333
silly God

187
00:11:45,333 --> 00:11:46,000
okay

188
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:51,166

before this pray pod thing, I want to check if Santa's coal is still there


189
00:11:51,966 --> 00:11:53,566
that's not funny though

190
00:11:53,766 --> 00:11:56,300
how do we power our boilers now

191
00:11:56,500 --> 00:12:00,900
shall we be bad or good kids to receive some coal next year

192
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:03,166

let's try with some pray


193
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,833
how does that works

194
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:10,233
the instructions seems pretty hard

195
00:12:11,066 --> 00:12:13,766
please give me some steam

196
00:12:16,066 --> 00:12:17,000
okay

197
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,466
double that

198
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:22,800
but how do we produce steam

199
00:12:23,033 --> 00:12:25,266
can we have a God blessed boiler

200
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:28,633
please help me God

201
00:12:29,766 --> 00:12:30,666
okay

202
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:35,600
is this a boilers that runs on holy water and God's light?

203
00:12:36,633 --> 00:12:38,600
please help me

204
00:12:38,833 --> 00:12:40,166
enlighten me

205
00:12:41,233 --> 00:12:46,433
maybe this time the answer is not above us but below us

206
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:02,800
wait what what happened okay

207
00:13:02,833 --> 00:13:04,900
this is not funny anymore

208
00:13:05,666 --> 00:13:07,033
is this a dream

209
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,166
an isekai

210
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:11,300
or what I have an idea

211
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,766
we take this magic wand

212
00:13:12,766 --> 00:13:16,766
and start building a nice looking steam setup using magic

213
00:13:16,766 --> 00:13:18,100
let's do it

214
00:14:34,366 --> 00:14:35,833
and here we go

215
00:00:00,166 --> 00:00:00,966
嗨！

216
00:00:01,400 --> 00:00:05,100
今天我们要开始一项简单却漫长的任务

217
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:08,300
在GTNH中制作星门

218
00:00:09,366 --> 00:00:12,166
这个包以极低的难度闻名

219
00:00:12,166 --> 00:00:15,000
所以让我们用极限模式玩吧

220
00:00:15,366 --> 00:00:18,633
因为我们有极低的概率嗝屁

221
00:00:18,666 --> 00:00:21,400
所以要做的就是加载备份

222
00:00:23,266 --> 00:00:26,866
我们要做的第一件事就是处理掉那本书

223
00:00:26,866 --> 00:00:28,233

因为看书很无聊


224
00:00:28,233 --> 00:00:31,100
而且背包也没有空闲位置留给它

225
00:00:31,566 --> 00:00:34,600
时间也不允许我们这么做

226
00:00:36,466 --> 00:00:40,400
现在可以继续找一个绿草茵茵的地方了

227
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:42,833
然后开始挖出地下室

228
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:47,800

既然我们找到了一片草地


229
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:51,166
可以开始找东西来做床了

230
00:00:56,100 --> 00:00:59,433

这包比原版好一点


231
00:00:59,433 --> 00:01:02,000
但还是不够现实

232
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:05,300
床只需要一些羊毛和木头

233
00:01:05,633 --> 00:01:10,266
不需要螺丝、胶水或任何东西来将其固定在一起

234
00:01:10,633 --> 00:01:13,500
可能是用魔法固定的

235
00:01:13,866 --> 00:01:19,833
无论如何，让我们在夜晚到来之前开始收集所需的资源

236
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:26,466
有了床，我们可以做些工具

237
00:01:26,866 --> 00:01:30,400
可以更快地收集材料

238
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:34,033
我们把地下室挖到石头层

239
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:40,300
别忘了这个包还有一些任务

240
00:01:40,666 --> 00:01:42,366
让我们看看

241
00:01:45,266 --> 00:01:48,000
当然，我不会读它

242
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:54,966
我们只完成星门路上的必要任务

243
00:02:00,966 --> 00:02:02,966
经过一整天的工作

244
00:02:02,966 --> 00:02:06,400

我们一边看着日落一边入睡


245
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:09,233
然后早餐吃个苹果

246
00:02:09,233 --> 00:02:11,600
医生远离我

247
00:02:12,666 --> 00:02:15,833

我们有了避难所和资源


248
00:02:15,833 --> 00:02:20,266
可以开始研究书中的神交给我们的任务

249
00:02:20,633 --> 00:02:23,200
由于现在我们才开始跟进进度

250
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:28,200

我们必须再做一次大半我们做过的东西


251
00:02:31,233 --> 00:02:34,200
我们现在先种点吃的

252
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:37,966
用它们来祭祀书中的神

253
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:40,800
既然我们在玩极限模式

254
00:02:40,833 --> 00:02:43,566
我们要吃素了

255
00:02:43,966 --> 00:02:44,966
这样的话

256
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,766
僵尸和骷髅将不会攻击我们

257
00:02:47,766 --> 00:02:50,500
因为他们会把我们视为一个已经死亡的实体

258
00:02:55,966 --> 00:02:59,433
看来书中的神不会喜欢我们的饮食

259
00:02:59,666 --> 00:03:02,100
祂要我们做一把剑

260
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:04,000
杀死一些可怜的动物

261
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,766

原因成谜


262
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:09,266
我们没有对抗神明的力量

263
00:03:09,266 --> 00:03:11,600
所以我们就照祂说的做

264
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,233
应诸神之命

265
00:03:15,233 --> 00:03:18,566
我们要杀六头猪与六头羊

266
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,066
经过一整天的战斗

267
00:03:22,066 --> 00:03:24,833

我们最需要的就是睡上一觉奖励自己


268
00:03:24,833 --> 00:03:28,433
忘记上帝让我们做的所有残忍的事

269
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,766

也可能忘不了


270
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:37,166
我们将整晚思考我们拳头落下所造成的残忍

271
00:03:37,366 --> 00:03:42,800
我们不应该扔掉在创造此世界获得的圣书

272
00:03:43,166 --> 00:03:46,700
我们用剩下的时间挖一个更好的地下室

273
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:51,200
看来诸神接受了我们的歉意

274
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:53,833
正如你从神的信息中看到的

275
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:58,200

是时候回到地表


276
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,866

透一透气


277
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:05,433
看来诸神赐予了我们一些蛛丝

278
00:04:05,466 --> 00:04:09,766
我们不会忘记刚刚收到的这份不可思议的礼物

279
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:17,166
我们现在可以去收集更多通往星门所需的资源了

280
00:04:17,166 --> 00:04:19,200
像一些木头和一些燧石

281
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:23,466
我们必须小心不要让木头浮在空中

282
00:04:23,466 --> 00:04:26,033
否则众神又要生我们的气了

283
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:33,700
我们也可以开始在地下室上面建一栋漂亮的房子

284
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:36,633

别人就不会鄙视我们了


285
00:04:39,366 --> 00:04:43,200
经过一整天的工作，我们终于可以睡觉了

286
00:04:45,233 --> 00:04:51,066
今天我们要探索书中诸神赋予我们的美丽世界

287
00:04:51,466 --> 00:04:54,800
实际上我们正在寻找一些有用的资源

288
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:58,266
也许能帮助我们完成建造星门的任务

289
00:05:00,266 --> 00:05:05,233
我们在路上找到了一些橡胶和粘土的来源

290
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:10,466
在所有的探索之后

291
00:05:10,466 --> 00:05:11,766
我们要睡觉了

292
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:14,600
哦，上帝，不

293
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,433
为什么

294
00:05:19,666 --> 00:05:23,966

这应该昭示了我们应该多装修一下地下室


295
00:05:24,366 --> 00:05:28,300
我们必须让它看起来像一只苦力怕在里面爆炸了

296
00:05:30,466 --> 00:05:33,200
现在这里太暗了

297
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:37,400
我们唯一的救世主可能是我们的老朋友NEI

298
00:05:37,666 --> 00:05:41,033
问问他怎么做发光棒

299
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:49,033
我们很幸运，我们可以将之前找到的树脂
与神给我们的蛛丝一起使用

300
00:05:49,033 --> 00:05:51,633
制作神圣发光的棍子

301
00:05:51,966 --> 00:05:54,700
它们是神圣的，因为永远不会燃烧殆尽

302
00:05:56,400 --> 00:06:01,966
让我们花几秒钟来欣赏我们的地下室有多漂亮

303
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:04,600
没有苦力怕在这爆炸过

304
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,400
然而

305
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:06,766
这里住着一只苦力怕

306
00:06:09,166 --> 00:06:12,100
众神奖励我们更多的蛛丝

307
00:06:16,166 --> 00:06:18,300
现在我们可以收集一些粘土

308
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:29,566

建起我们的农村


309
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:33,100
我们将在那里种植棉花和小麦

310
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:36,800
这样可以自给自足线

311
00:06:36,866 --> 00:06:40,633
不需要依靠神的恩赐

312
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,833

小麦能用在未来的奶牛圈建设里


313
00:06:43,833 --> 00:06:46,400

也可以用来当食物


314
00:06:46,633 --> 00:06:49,633
有了新获得的食物和光源

315
00:06:49,633 --> 00:06:52,666
我们可以去地下收集一些材料

316
00:06:52,666 --> 00:06:55,400

这样我们就可以开始建设我们的工业


317
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:58,233
现在我们有了所有这些资源

318
00:06:58,266 --> 00:07:01,533
我想现在是休息的好时机

319
00:07:01,533 --> 00:07:04,866
然后开始建造污染工厂

320
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:07,433
现在是时候开始

321
00:07:07,433 --> 00:07:07,833
补兑

322
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,700
我在哪里？这是一场梦吗？

323
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:14,166

这看上去就是我的基地计划


324
00:07:14,433 --> 00:07:16,766

这肯定是一个梦


325
00:07:16,766 --> 00:07:19,266

用来解释我计划的梦


326
00:07:20,100 --> 00:07:20,833
那就这样吧

327
00:07:20,833 --> 00:07:23,433
在这里我们将有一个冶炼厂

328
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:27,666
用于制作青铜工具和第一批模具

329
00:07:28,166 --> 00:07:32,766
旁边是焦炉，用来制造杂酚油

330
00:07:33,966 --> 00:07:37,300
现在我想我们应该出去碰些草

331
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:39,500
并规划我们的自动化农场

332
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:43,700
等等，这棵树有点可疑

333
00:07:44,566 --> 00:07:48,400
显然圣诞老人给了我们一些煤

334
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,700
但看起来这煤有点劣质了

335
00:07:51,966 --> 00:07:55,700
我希望它对我们的锅炉来说仍然足够好

336
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:59,066
等等，刚刚发生了什么？

337
00:07:59,366 --> 00:08:02,000
它不应该破坏告示牌

338
00:08:02,466 --> 00:08:08,600
现在让我们把这些几乎变质成闪亮垃圾的煤加热

339
00:08:09,233 --> 00:08:13,600
我们也许可以通过加热把它还原成可燃煤

340
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:17,766
但那可能需要一整桶杂酚油

341
00:08:18,266 --> 00:08:19,233
拜托上帝

342
00:08:19,233 --> 00:08:22,766
变回可燃煤

343
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:33,566
好吧，我不知道这是否有效

344
00:08:33,566 --> 00:08:36,600
但看起来我们还是可以烧掉那些东西

345
00:08:37,433 --> 00:08:38,233
现在

346
00:08:38,300 --> 00:08:40,000
这里有一个锅炉

347
00:08:40,266 --> 00:08:42,900
它燃烧煤炭产生蒸汽

348
00:08:45,866 --> 00:08:49,400
太好了，它接受了我们的烂煤

349
00:08:49,566 --> 00:08:51,700
现在我们得给它一些水

350
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,266
让我们去取一些

351
00:08:55,866 --> 00:08:59,300
我们不想用沼泽里的浑水

352
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:02,600
我们要去河里收集干净的水

353
00:09:11,933 --> 00:09:14,433
现在锅炉有点温度了

354
00:09:14,433 --> 00:09:16,500
终于可以加水了

355
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:19,000
这样我们就会立即得到蒸汽

356
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,266
等等怎么回事

357
00:09:21,466 --> 00:09:23,633
怎么都黑了

358
00:09:23,766 --> 00:09:25,800
这是什么鬼梦

359
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,900
我终于醒来了吗

360
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:32,466
现在我们在哪

361
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:35,866
看来我们找到了通往天堂的路

362
00:09:36,666 --> 00:09:37,300
噢，哇

363
00:09:37,300 --> 00:09:42,000

所以看起来天堂是核驱动的


364
00:09:43,666 --> 00:09:46,833
但看起来这没有正确设置

365
00:09:47,033 --> 00:09:49,300
让我帮助你，上帝

366
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,966
如果我们把单元堆得更近

367
00:09:52,966 --> 00:09:54,866
输出应该更高

368
00:09:54,866 --> 00:09:58,033
效率也会更高

369
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,466
像那样

370
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:14,700
现在我们得关掉这个该死的装置

371
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:17,700
等等

372
00:10:18,066 --> 00:10:19,700
那是什么音乐

373
00:10:19,766 --> 00:10:21,566
它从哪里传来？

374
00:10:23,433 --> 00:10:27,866
一个人怎么可能会死在天堂里？

375
00:10:28,033 --> 00:10:30,233
现在会发生什么？

376
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:34,200
伙计们我有个B计划

377
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:39,200
我们只要重新加载做这个奇怪的梦之前的备份

378
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,300
让我们开始吧

379
00:10:41,266 --> 00:10:42,166
好的

380
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:45,166
我看不到我们的星门任务

381
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:48,466
我们要么进入一个通用的世界

382
00:10:48,466 --> 00:10:51,800
或者，是的，让我们选择方案B

383
00:10:53,466 --> 00:10:56,700
现在我们得想个办法解决这个冰上风筝的事

384
00:10:57,700 --> 00:11:00,066
这里看起来像一个控制室

385
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:02,633
在这里

386
00:11:02,633 --> 00:11:05,800

我们去随机打乱一下这些个拉杆


387
00:11:06,033 --> 00:11:10,833
那样的话上帝会生我们的气而把我们送回地下室

388
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:14,066
那个看起来很奇怪的管子是什么？

389
00:11:14,366 --> 00:11:16,733
什么东西刚刚穿过？

390
00:11:16,733 --> 00:11:17,466
随便了

391
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,433
好吧

392
00:11:19,666 --> 00:11:22,633
看起来这次什么都没发生

393
00:11:22,766 --> 00:11:26,366
让我们四处寻找宇宙旅行机器

394
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,500
看起来是这个

395
00:11:29,666 --> 00:11:31,300
让我们试一试

396
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:39,600
嘿

397
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:40,600
它起作用了

398
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:43,766
我回到了我梦中的世界

399
00:11:43,866 --> 00:11:45,333
傻上帝

400
00:11:45,333 --> 00:11:46,000
好吧

401
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:51,166
在祈求资源之前，我想检查一下圣诞老人的煤是否还在那里

402
00:11:51,966 --> 00:11:53,566
这一点也不好笑

403
00:11:53,766 --> 00:11:56,300
我们现在如何为锅炉供电？

404
00:11:56,500 --> 00:12:00,900
明年该变坏呢？还是成为好孩子再获得些煤

405
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:03,166
让我们再祈求一下

406
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,833
这是怎么回事？

407
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:10,233

给的指示太难了


408
00:12:11,066 --> 00:12:13,766
请给我一些蒸汽

409
00:12:16,066 --> 00:12:17,000
好吧

410
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,466
再来一个

411
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:22,800
但是我们如何产生蒸汽呢？

412
00:12:23,033 --> 00:12:25,266
我们能有一个上帝保佑的锅炉吗？

413
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:28,633
请帮帮我上帝

414
00:12:29,766 --> 00:12:30,666
好吧

415
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:35,600
这是一个用圣水和上帝之光运行的锅炉吗？

416
00:12:36,633 --> 00:12:38,600
请帮帮我

417
00:12:38,833 --> 00:12:40,166
开导我

418
00:12:41,233 --> 00:12:46,433
也许这次答案不在我们上面而是在下面

419
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:02,800
等等发生了什么事

420
00:13:02,833 --> 00:13:04,900
这一点都不好笑了

421
00:13:05,666 --> 00:13:07,033
这是梦吗

422
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,166
一个异世界

423
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:11,300
或者我有个主意

424
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,766
我们拿着这根魔杖

425
00:13:12,766 --> 00:13:16,766
开始用魔法建造一个漂亮的蒸汽装置

426
00:13:16,766 --> 00:13:18,100
让我们开始吧

427
00:14:34,366 --> 00:14:35,833
完事

428
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:43,766
（我只是在开玩笑捏
嘻嘻
——上帝）

429
00:11:51,166 --> 00:11:52,600
（还没到圣诞节呢
笑死）

430
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:10,233
（祈祷
然后
跳）

431
00:13:01,500 --> 00:13:03,466
（我又在开玩笑了
嘻嘻
——上帝）

432
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:09,033
（去看《想要成为影之实力者！》）

433
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:43,766
（试试许愿池→）

434
00:13:01,500 --> 00:13:03,466
（不管怎么说
你的祈愿已经
被实现了）

